# Windows-10-Theme

1. Create a restore point, Simply search for Create a restore point
Select your windows system (C) drive, Configure
Select Turn on system protection & set max usage to 20%
Apply & OK.
Select Create option given below Configure and create a restore point.

2. Download and Run ThemeTool.exe as administrator
Select Yes
Select Hook SystemSettings, Hook LogonUI, Rename DefaultColors
INSTALL & REBOOT.

3. Download Paranoid android window 10 theme
Extract the zip, Open the extracted zip folder
Go to Windows 10 Themes folder
Go to Pure Dark folder
Select all files and copy to c:\windows\resources\themes

again, run ThemeTool.exe as administrator
Select yes
Select nebula & Patch
again, select Ignore background and Ignore cursor
Patch and apply

4. Create a new folder in localdisk c:\ and name it Win10
Cut & Paste your ThemeTool.exe to Win10 folder

5. Download sweet paranoia icon pack
Extract the zip, Open the extracted zip folder
Delete 7TSP, Read me and Sweet Paranoia Preview
Open iPack folder and rename Sweet Paranoia.exe.remove to Sweet Paranoia.exe
Run Sweet Paranoia.exe
Accept, Next, Select Patch all files > Next > Yes (It might take few minutes depending on your PC specs)
FINISH.

6. Go back to extracted folder > sweet paranoia icon theme > Cut & Paste candy-icons folder to localdisk c:\

7. Download and extract OldNewExplorer
Cut & Paste OldNewExplorer folder to c:\Win10\ > Open OldNewExplorer and Run OldNewExplorer as administrator
IN APPEARANCE
Select Use command bar instead of Ribbon and the following 3 options starting with HIDE, Unselect all other already selected options except the one you did.
INSTALL & Close.

8. Go to Taskbar settings > Use small taskbar buttons > Set the taskbar location on screen to Top.

9. Download startisback and paranoidOrbs
Run startisback and Select Install for me, 
wait till it get installed then select configure startisback now

In Appearance, Select Second Dark Menu > Select First Dark Explorer & Apply (DON'T CLOSE THE SETTING YET)
Extract paranoidOrbs and Open the folder
Go to startisback settings and click on + icon
Choose the folder where you extacted paranoidOrbs and select Lace3.png > Select the start icon as Lace
Apply & OK

10. Right click on taskbar and unselect Show cortana button, Show taskview button
Again right click on taskbar and set Search > Hidden

11. Download the new cursor
Extract the files and Open Breeze_Snow_x2 > Right click on Install.inf and Install
In mouse properties settings select the mouse cursor you just installed
Apply & OK.

12. Download and Set wallpaper.
